  <brief_title>Study Medication Adherence and Its Determinants in Chronic Disease Through the Example of Methotrexate in Chronic Inflammatory Rheumatism</brief_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Centre Hospitalier Universitaire de Nīmes</agency>
