      <textblock>
        patients with chronic inflammatory rheumatism (rheumatoid arthritis, spondyloarthritis and
        psoriatic arthritis) treated by methotrexate in the department of rheumatology in the Nîmes
        University Hospital
      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  treated by methotrexate

          -  patients with chronic inflammatory rheumatism (rheumatoid arthritis, spondyloarthritis
             and psoriatic arthritis)

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  methotrexate for other diseases
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
